statements: SELECT * FROM website_navigation_patterns WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, page_visited FROM website_navigation_patterns WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';

SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_navigation_patterns ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM user_navigation_patterns GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_visits > 3;

SELECT w.username, p.page_url, n.event_type FROM website_users w JOIN page_views p ON w.user_id = p.user_id JOIN navigation_events n ON p.view_id = n.view_id WHERE n.event_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-01';
SELECT u.username, s.start_timestamp, s.end_timestamp FROM website_users u JOIN user_sessions s ON u.user_id = s.user_id WHERE s.end_timestamp IS NOT NULL ORDER BY s.start_timestamp DESC;
